<h2>Tour Overview</h2>
<h3>Voted Chicago's Best Tour, this Hop On Hop Off Trolley Tour has long been the gold standard for touring downtown Chicago. The tour gives you transportation to the most famous Chicago attractions on Red & Green Trolleys and Big Red Double Decker Buses.</h3>
<p>The Explore Tour allows you to hop off to visit a Chicago attraction or museum, shop, dine, and just explore as you have 3 full days to use it. With the same ticket, you also get seasonal access to three Neighborhood Tours (North, West and South) as well as the Nights and Lights Tour (May through September).</p>
<p>Your tour can begin at any of the 14 stops in the downtown area. Stops include: Millennium Park, the Art Institute, Field Museum, Navy Pier, John Hancock Observatory, Skydeck Chicago, and the River North district, among many others.</p>
<p>Take your time and hop-on/hop-off for three days!</p>
<p><strong>Length:</strong> Valid for 3 days</p>
<strong>Time:</strong>
<ul>
	<li>Daily departures from 9:00 am to 5:00 pm - Mid-March through early November</li>
	<li>Daily departures from 9:00 am to 4:00 pm - Early November through mid-March</li>
	<li><em>Time on availability calendar is for booking purposes only and reflects the first tour departure time each day.</em></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Summary:</strong> Pickups available only at designated trolley stops. Neighborhood Tours and Night Tour only available May through September. Child rate applies to children ages 3 to 12. Children under 3 are free. <br><strong>Please order online or call 888-881-3284 to order or for more information.</strong></p>
<p>There is a $6.95 USD processing fee per order. This is a flat fee regardless of the number of tickets or tours purchased on an order. There is a service charge per ticket. This charge will be reflected in your summary before you checkout. The total shown includes any and all taxes, fuel surcharges, and service fees. There are no additional charges, unless otherwise specified.</p>